Place Cline extension in secondary sidebar (right side) by default

This patch modifies VS Code to:
1. Register Cline's view container in the AuxiliaryBar (secondary sidebar on the right)
   instead of the primary Sidebar (left side)
2. Set the secondary sidebar default width to 40% of the screen (max 600px)
3. Force the auxiliary bar to be visible on every page load (overrides stored state)

